00:57:36,244 --> 00:57:37,829
You were looking at me
when I was sleeping.

809
00:58:09,611 --> 00:58:10,612
Bye.

810
00:58:13,156 --> 00:58:14,532
Come back home safely.

811
00:58:18,620 --> 00:58:19,496
Okay.

812
00:58:22,123 --> 00:58:22,957
I'll be back.

813
00:59:31,859 --> 00:59:32,902
Bye.

814
00:59:35,113 --> 00:59:36,155
Dan.

815
00:59:53,548 --> 00:59:55,466
Yes, call her right now.

816
00:59:55,675 --> 00:59:56,801
Tell her to be there.

817
01:00:20,658 --> 01:00:22,160
Hello, I'm Lee Yeon-seo.

818
01:00:23,911 --> 01:00:24,996
You know me, don't you?

819
01:00:25,830 --> 01:00:27,040
Of course, you do.

820
01:00:28,041 --> 01:00:30,543
You have to know me.
Think about everything you did to me.

821
01:00:31,919 --> 01:00:34,839
You made me an orphan at the age of 17,
made me blind so I couldn't dance,

822
01:00:35,673 --> 01:00:37,300
and you took away my one and only Mr. Cho.

823
01:00:39,552 --> 01:00:43,348
And all of my relatives
are dying to kill me.

824
01:00:45,558 --> 01:00:46,934
Don't you think that's too much?

825
01:00:47,852 --> 01:00:48,853
But I didn't come

826
01:00:49,604 --> 01:00:51,189
to complain about that.

827
01:00:51,981 --> 01:00:54,400
I'm all right now
because you sent Dan to me.

828
01:00:55,610 --> 01:00:56,986
I'm all right.

829
01:00:59,822 --> 01:01:01,366
But you can't do that to Dan.

830
01:01:02,408 --> 01:01:05,119
I'm angry enough that he died
a horrible death as Seong-u.

831
01:01:05,703 --> 01:01:07,080
What did he do wrong?

832
01:01:07,497 --> 01:01:08,748
His mission was to make me love.

833
01:01:09,248 --> 01:01:10,416
And I love Dan.

834
01:01:11,000 --> 01:01:13,711
I don't know what kind of love
you wanted to see,

835
01:01:13,961 --> 01:01:16,923
but I am in love with Dan.

836
01:01:18,549 --> 01:01:19,384
But...

837
01:01:20,802 --> 01:01:22,595
But why does he have to dissipate?

838
01:01:24,597 --> 01:01:26,641
If you have any conscience,
you cannot do this.

839
01:01:27,016 --> 01:01:28,434
You can't do this!

840
01:01:52,875 --> 01:01:54,377
You like fairness, don't you?

841
01:01:56,379 --> 01:01:57,630
You take one thing

842
01:01:58,923 --> 01:02:00,007
and give another.

843
01:02:02,593 --> 01:02:03,553
Right?

844
01:02:36,711 --> 01:02:37,670
I'm shocked.

845
01:02:38,171 --> 01:02:39,213
You had a plan.

846
01:02:40,673 --> 01:02:41,716
I told you

847
01:02:42,216 --> 01:02:45,052
that I will stop you myself
if you try to do

848
01:02:46,053 --> 01:02:47,263
anything foolish again.

849
01:02:56,105 --> 01:02:57,482
I am not curious about

850
01:02:58,357 --> 01:02:59,442
the providence

851
01:03:01,194 --> 01:03:02,195
or the plan.

852
01:03:14,582 --> 01:03:16,250
If I must kill someone

853
01:03:17,960 --> 01:03:19,629
for the sake of the one I wish to save,

854
01:03:22,048 --> 01:03:23,049
then I will

855
01:03:25,426 --> 01:03:26,803
gladly commit that sin.

856
01:03:31,974 --> 01:03:33,184
Take everything from me.

857
01:03:34,393 --> 01:03:35,394
Anything.

858
01:03:38,689 --> 01:03:40,274
I can give it to you gladly.

859
01:03:41,442 --> 01:03:42,443
-To...
-To...

860
01:03:43,319 --> 01:03:44,737
-...save him.
-...save her.

